giada ( your hardcore looping machine )

Giada is a free, minimal, hardcore audio tool for djs and live       
performers. Load up to 32 samples, choose to play them in single mode
(drum machine) or loop mode (sequencer) and start the show with your 
computer keyboard as a controller.                                   

Homepage: http://www.monocasual.com/giada/
Docs: http://www.monocasual.com/giada/documentation.php
